dct_title_s: Routes from Los Angeles to Santa Barbara
dct_description_sm: Automobile Club of Southern California ; E.J.B.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Oriented with north toward upper right.
Shows city plans, roads, railroads, ocean.
Indicates distances from Los Angeles and Santa Barbara.
Belongs to a series of strip maps showing roads in California.
